data.enText: the back part of the leg between the ankle and the knee
a young animal of some other type such as a young elephant or whale

tr: young of various large placental mammals e.g. whale or giraffe or elephant or buffalo
the muscular back part of the shank
fine leather from the skin of a calf

value.def: Some other young animals, including elephants and whales, are called calves .
Your calf is the thick part at the back of your leg, between your ankle and your knee.

trans: 牛犊恋；早恋；初恋；少年时代的恋爱；晓丽因早恋
小牛皮；头层小牛皮；犊牛皮；牛犊皮；仔牛革
